Look at Credit Suisse Trust Commodity Return Strategy Fund (CCRSX)


Zacks Equity Research
                June 05, 2017

CCRSX 

Trades from
$1











 









Read MoreHide Full Article










Credit Suisse Trust Commodity Return Strategy Fund  (CCRSX  -  Free Report)	 seeks high level of positive return, which are relative to the performance of the Bloomberg Commodity Index Total Return (the "BCOM Index"). The advisor of CCRSX focuses on investing the fund’s assets in a variety of fixed income securities and commodity-linked derivative instruments. CCRSX is a non-diversified fund.

	This Zacks Rank #5 (Strong Sell) was incepted in February 2006 and is managed by  Credit Suisse. CCRSX carries an expense ratio of 1.05% and requires a minimal initial investment of $0.

